1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,880
Yuki, don't tell me you...

2
00:00:05,710 --> 00:00:07,420
What is it?

3
00:00:09,300 --> 00:00:10,890
...actually see me as a big brother?

4
00:00:10,890 --> 00:00:13,470
Huh? Get over yourself.

5
00:00:13,470 --> 00:00:14,600
Ow!

6
00:00:15,140 --> 00:00:16,600
Alright, let's begin.

7
00:00:16,600 --> 00:00:20,600
I think a base is all you really need for everyday wear.
So let's start with some toner.

8
00:00:20,600 --> 00:00:22,480
Here.

9
00:00:23,610 --> 00:00:25,070
Don't rub too hard.

10
00:00:25,070 --> 00:00:26,990
Okay.

11
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:30,910
So... what's base makeup?

12
00:00:30,910 --> 00:00:35,830
You start with a primer, then use concealer
to cover up acne scars, spots, and dark circles.

13
00:00:36,120 --> 00:00:38,410
Got it. I'll give it a try.

14
00:00:40,250 --> 00:00:41,250
(Spritzes)

15
00:00:41,250 --> 00:00:43,590
You goof! You're not supposed to spray it right on your face!

16
00:00:43,590 --> 00:00:45,050
Oh, you're not?

17
00:00:45,050 --> 00:00:48,170
Sigh... And that's way too much.

18
00:00:48,170 --> 00:00:49,260
Sorry.

19
00:00:49,260 --> 00:00:52,260
No, it's my fault.
I should have shown you first.

20
00:00:53,550 --> 00:00:55,640
Let me get that for you. Don't move.

21
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:57,100
Okay.

22
00:01:07,650 --> 00:01:13,280
(Come to think of it, he's really handsome.
His eyelashes are so long, and his lips look so soft.)

23
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:17,540
(There's no way he's not popular.
I bet he's kissed someone with those lips before.)

24
00:01:22,710 --> 00:01:24,710
Makoto, what's with your mouth?

25
00:01:24,710 --> 00:01:26,460
Oh, uh, sorry.
